title: Episode 326: Everybody Hoein' (Feat. Sleepy Hallow)
itunes:title: Episode 326: Everybody Hoein' (Feat. Sleepy Hallow)
description:
NY Rapper, Sleepy Hallow joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote the deluxe version of his latest album 'Still Sleep?' The crew discusses a range of topics including his potential sex tape, his lack of interest in women playing with his b*lls, his insecurities regarding social media, and much more. Sleepy believes that flowers are the nicest gift he's ever gotten for a lady...Would you rather designer things or flowers? Enjoy!
